title: GetObjectIDFromContents (Function)
text:
FUNCTION GetObjectIDFromContents : CmpBACnet.IEC_BACNET_OBJECT_ID
Tries to evaluate property contents as IEC_BACNET_OBJECT_ID data type.
If the contents are not of type IEC_BACNET_OBJECT_ID an IEC_BACNET_OBJECT_ID(typ = _OBJ_MAX_SIZE, instNumber = 0) is returned.

rows.Name: conts
rows.Comment: The contents to be evaluated as IEC_BACNET_OBJECT_ID.
